readable.content: A man in a turban looks at two police officers who are near a tent and a pile of refuse . Men with hats on stand outside of a white tent . Turbaned man and two police officers stand in front of a white canopy and a pile of garbage bags Two officers with orange jackets stand outside a white tent with onlookers . Two police officers observe while a crowd gathers outside a white tarp .
